# 系统上下文图（System Context）

## L1: 系统上下文

```mermaid
graph TD
    User[用户] -->|配置规则| Frontend[Vue3 前端]
    User -->|查看进度| Frontend
    Frontend -->|API调用| Backend[Next.js API]
    Backend -->|启动任务| Worker[Worker线程]
    Worker -->|生成密钥| PGP[PGP库]
    Worker -->|推送进度| Backend
    Backend -->|SSE| Frontend
    Backend -->|存储| SQLite[(SQLite)]
    Worker -->|发现密钥| Backend
    Backend -->|返回公钥| Frontend
```

## L2: 容器图

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph 前端容器
        Vue[Vue 3 App]
        Pinia[Pinia Store]
        Chart[Chart.js]
    end

    subgraph 后端容器
        NextJS[Next.js API]
        RouteHandler[API Routes]
        SSEHandler[SSE Handler]
        WorkerPool[Worker Pool]
        MiningWorker[Mining Worker]
    end

    subgraph 数据层
        SQLite[(SQLite)]
    end

    RouteHandler -->|创建任务| WorkerPool
    SSEHandler -->|推送| WorkerPool
    WorkerPool -->|执行| MiningWorker
    MiningWorker -->|读写| SQLite
    Vue -->|HTTP/SSE| NextJS
    Pinia -->|状态| Vue
    Chart -->|图表| Vue
```